data.description: Welcome home to this newly renovated ranch home on a large corner lot. New to this home is interior and exterior paint, new Luxury Vinyl Plank, New granite countertops in kitchen and all new stainless steel appliances, new HVAC, new Water Heater. Large living room with cozy fireplace and deck off back of home with seperate dining room. Primary bedroom and ensuite bathroom and 2 secondary bedrooms with hall bathroom. Dont miss it!!!
